actions.message:
More info on:
             .rules - for showing rules.
             .contact - more info about contact.
             .staff - for showing name of all staff.
             .bots  - list of bots.
             .random ? ? - generates random number between those 2.
             !rank - to show you what rank are you.
             !levels - to see everyone's level and customize your rank card.
    MusicBot:
             /play (YT-link) - to play your music.
             /stop - pause the music.
             /resume - resume your stopped music.
             /skip - skip the music.
       Staff:
             .staffinfo - info for staff.
